metadata.name: Future
metadata.description:
This is a difficult time for all of us, I want each of us to understand that the future lies in space, and it is important to understand that people must find new lands and new life. I want and dream to meet the people who are working on launching infinity. The search for a bright future for humanity, that is the main task must be accomplished. This token is dedicated to all of you. It is a white sheet, an invitation card to communicate with me. I am creating a community around me. Everyone who acquires this piece is my family. This piece is worth keeping, it is valid indefinitely, it means you will have access to hidden information about me. Your enigmatic Masha Kova. 

Appreciate, love, remember... (1/4)
